</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/01d131dfd7673938b947072a13a9744fe997e632" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.338ex; width:1.09ex; height:1.676ex;" alt="{\displaystyle s}"/></span> is a real number ("scalar"), and <span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt445" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"B"}}' id="mwBEc"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle B}">
