        </msup>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\displaystyle {\text{MultiheadAttention}}(Q,K,V)={\text{Concat}}_{i\in [n_{\text{heads}}]}\left({\text{Attention}}(XW_{i}^{Q},XW_{i}^{K},XW_{i}^{V})\right)W^{O}}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/02afa45e87322c7c0b4919c8ba934861b54fc06e" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-display mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -1.838ex; width:86.906ex; height:4.843ex;" alt="{\displaystyle {\text{MultiheadAttention}}(Q,K,V)={\text{Concat}}_{i\in [n_{\text{heads}}]}\left({\text{Attention}}(XW_{i}^{Q},XW_{i}^{K},XW_{i}^{V})\right)W^{O}}"/></span>with Multi-Query Attention, there is just one <span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt497" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"W^K, W^V"}}' id="mwBLs"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle W^{K},W^{V}}">
