</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/e6c8b294488a1ddcc0380c8a8cb75b3410fe7ede" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.671ex; width:2.384ex; height:2.509ex;" alt="{\displaystyle {\tilde {x}}_{2}}"/></span> are verified by GPT-3 as what it would have picked, then those are kept, but <span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt524" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"\\tilde{x}_3"}}' id="mwBOw"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle {\tilde {x}}_{3}}">
  <semantics>
