</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/2de3175aa437329b2c5b3a3fc1167be15882b81d" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.671ex; width:2.384ex; height:2.509ex;" alt="{\displaystyle {\tilde {x}}_{3}}"/></span> is not, so <span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt525" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"\\tilde{x}_3, \\tilde{x}_4"}}' id="mwBO0"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle {\tilde {x}}_{3},{\tilde {x}}_{4}}">
  <semantics>
